NTSET Protector
A specialist in dealing with supernatural threats, demons, and Rifts phenomena.
NTSET (North American Territorial Supernatural Enforcement Team) operatives
carry mystically-warded weapons and are trained in the lore of demons, monsters,
and magic. They are the front line against the supernatural on Rifts Earth.

NTSET Protectors are trained in lore, tracking, detection, and heavy weapons.
Their silver ammunition and warded armor make them effective against creatures
that laugh off conventional firepower. Skill picks come from Espionage, Military,
Physical, Lore, and W.P. categories.

Attribute requirements: IQ 10, PS 12, PE 12.
Starting equipment: Mystically-warded body armor, two energy weapons,
silver ammunition, anti-supernatural kit, radio, and NTSET credentials.
